dge ok' : 'ASSERT progress badge missing')\nconsole.log(visibleText.includes('Step 5 of 6. 3 of 3 narration segments are durable already. Estimated listening length 13 min.') ? 'ASSERT progress hint ok' : 'ASSERT progress hint missing')\nawait page.screenshot({ path: outputPath, fullPage: true })\nconsole.log(\"'`SCREENSHOT ${outputPath}`)\nawait browser.close()\nNODE'","aggregated_output":"[browser:error] Failed to load resource: the server responded with a status of 502 (Bad Gateway)\nASSERT progress badge ok\nASSERT progress hint ok\nSCREENSHOT /Users/kevin/code/storyteller/.artifacts/webapp-qa/prompt-75-audio-progress-ui.png\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
